{"tid":2426571,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"［試下再入紙上街好唔好？］劉頴匡：遺憾不能目睹港人再上街","createTime":"2021-02-28T07:26:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-28T08:48:03.000Z","uid":42194,"like":25,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"f1738cec5bf85319ca4a5b1c62672b6c49b5cdb1","tid":2426571,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:26:26.000Z","msg":"【最後的自由？】或被起訴還柙　劉頴匡：遺憾不能目睹港人再上街<br />\n<br />\n曾參與去年民主派「35+」初選的候選人，今年 1 月被指控違反國安法被捕，昨日陸續收警方通知，要求在本周日（28 日）「提前報到」，外界猜測屆時或被落案起訴，即時還柙。<br />\n<br />\n參選新界東初選的劉頴匡，配了一副全塑膠眼鏡，因為獄中不能配戴金屬眼鏡，「近視好深，唔戴眼鏡路都行唔到。」過去多次舉辦遊行，負責申請「不反對通知書」，他說自己的一個遺憾，是假如還柙甚至入獄，可能難以再親眼目睹港人走上街頭，示威遊行。<br />\n<br />\n他也說對女友有愧，「正常一個男朋友都諗緊點規劃將來。」<br />\n<br />\n睇片：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2NF0kr0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2NF0kr0&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3m9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=f9c033e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2NF0kr0</a><br />\n相關報道：<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2O8NBfO\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2O8NBfO&d=zAz8RNAQ9Ot7v23HNjWT3m9Dn5prBKp8mj11ELPip4s%3D&h=416a096c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2O8NBfO</a><br />\n<br />\n攝影：Nasha Chan<br />\n記者：林心怡<br />\n<br />\nVL 巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />= 再入紙上街，重啟街頭抗爭<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />= 不了"},{"pid":"bf7833af662a9997bd3ede6379f620530115c3a5","tid":2426571,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:27:03.000Z","msg":"推連登公投<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f179eccf45c4d1ee00c512f0f78a9d33fa87f78","tid":2426571,"uid":369011,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T07:27:12.000Z","msg":"都唔會批入黎做乜"},{"pid":"838109d55bed0757ca55e73c414946e80c3947cc","tid":2426571,"uid":42194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score